fields.name: ||Ability||
fields.value: ||Character Stats are randomized each time the character menu is opened. See Stats below.||

fields.name: ||Unlock||
fields.value:
||Required: Yellow Sign.
Choose your fastest character.
Choose the Green Acres stage with Hyper and Hurry.
Start going South-West as soon as you spawn until your screen is filled with green and and black lines.
Kill 128 of the Winged Giant Eyes. Kills add up through multiple runs.
Notice: This unlock does not make a jingle.||

fields.name: ||Stats||
fields.value:
||Ranges of the Randomized Stats:
Max Health: -3 to +97
Recovery: -0.5 to +1.0
Armor: +0 to +2
MoveSpeed: -200% to 0%
Might: -120% to +100%
Area: -140% to +260%
Speed: -120% to +80%
Duration: -130% to +170
Amount: +0 to +2
Cooldown: -120% to +80%
Luck: -120% to +80%
Growth: -120% to +80%
Greed: -120% to +80%
Curse: -105% to +95%
Magnet: -20% to +180%
Revivals: +0 to +2

If Max Health is below 0%, missingNo becomes invincible.
If MoveSpeed is below -100%, the controls become inverted.
If Growth is below -100%, missingNo cannot gain experience.
If Curse is below -100%, no enemies will appear at all.||
